East River, shoreline, west from Corlears (right) to Jackson Streets, showing Corlears Hook Park. On the left (adjoining the white building) is St. Mary's Roman Catholic School (with flag pole) and to its right (with gabled roof), St. Rose's Home, at the N.W. corner of Jackson and Front Streets.
